/// PancakeSwap V3 is a UniV3 fork but its `Swap` event has 2 extra trailing
/// non-indexed parameters: `protocolFeesToken0` and `protocolFeesToken1`.
/// These change the keccak256 of the canonical signature, producing a different
/// topic0 from UniV3.
///
/// # ABI verification
///
/// Source: github.com/pancakeswap/pancake-v3-contracts/projects/v3-core/contracts/
///         interfaces/pool/IPancakeV3PoolEvents.sol
/// Fetched: 2026-04-24 via WebFetch (raw.githubusercontent.com).
