    // PancakeSwap V3 factory PoolCreated event ABI is IDENTICAL to UniV3:
    //   event PoolCreated(address indexed token0, address indexed token1,
    //                     uint24 indexed fee, int24 tickSpacing, address pool)
    //
    // Source: IPancakeV3Factory.sol (pancakeswap/pancake-v3-contracts), fetched 2026-04-24.
    // The existing `try_decode_v3_pool_created` + `pool_created_to_pool_event` handle BSC
    // PancakeSwap V3 factory events without modification.
    // `pool_created_to_pool_event` already maps Chain::Bsc → DexKind::PancakeSwapV3.
    // No separate decoder is needed. Tests `bsc_pool_created_maps_to_pancake_v3_dex` above
    // verify the chain-sensitive DexKind mapping.
